title: Stella Creasy outs internet trolls in YouTube video clip
text: Stella Creasy outs internet trolls in YouTube video clip Friday, 4 September 2015 (12 minutes ago) Labour deputy leadership candidate reads out some of the offensive messages sent to her during her campaign The Labour deputy leadership candidate Stella Creasy has responded to internet trolls by releasing a video in which she reads out some of the offensive messages she has been sent during the campaign.Creasy admitted that ...
